#summary Detailed description of a system with functional requirements
#labels Phase-Requirements

<h1>User</h1>
<ul>
<li>Profile Page (uprofile.jsp)
<p>
Features: 
  * change password
  * info about the user
</p>

</li>

<li>Schedule Page (uschedule.jsp)
<p>
Features:
  * Calendar showing 5 weeks, divided into active|blocked parts (greyed out)
  * Clicking on a date will redirect to a day page. 
</p>

</li>
<li>Day Page (day.jsp)
<p>
Features:
  * Day have 24 cells to make a reservation.
  * Cells will be divided into: free cell (green), reserved cell by  active user (blue), reserved cell by other users (red)
  * Clicking on a free cell will fire "making reservation" function - result will be either success or exception
  * Clicking on a reserved by active user cell will fire "cancel reservation" function - when possible or exception
  * clicking on a reserved by other user cell will do nothing
</p>
</li>
<li>Statistics Page (statistics.jsp)
<p>
Features:
  * showing statistics of usage by active user in requested period (query to database)
</p>

</li>
</ul>

<h1>Supervisor</h1>
<p>Supervisor has all features as normal user has + additional features
</p>
<ul>
<li>Users Page (susers.jsp)
<p>
Features:
  * List of all users (grid view), with options for each user block|reset password|info about user
 

</p>
</li>
<li>
Calendar Page (sschedule.jsp)
<p>The same as normal user +
  *  Can cancel whole day (only previous day in the past)
  *  Can lock booking for the day
  *  Can unlock booking for the day
</p>
</li>

<li>Day Page (sday.jsp)
<p>
  *  Reserved cells can be cancelled (only previous day in the past)
  *  Lock window
  *  Unlock window
  
</p>
</li>
</ul>

